## 🚀 How to Run Locally

### 1. Install Dependencies
```bash
pip install pandas matplotlib seaborn streamlit plotly
Trending_Youtube_Videos_Insights.ipynb
streamlit run youtube_dashboard.py
YouTube_EDA_Report.pdf
📊 Sample Visualizations
🔥 Top 10 Trending Videos (bar chart)

📈 Views vs Likes (scatter plot with log scale)

🧠 Correlation Heatmap (views, likes, comments, dislikes)

💬 Top Tags (from 10,000 row sample)

⏰ Trending Time Heatmap (day vs hour)

📄 Exported Insights as printable PDF report

📌 Insights Uncovered
✅ Strong correlation between views and likes

✅ Tags like "music", "official", "challenge" dominate the trending list

✅ Engagement is highest on weekends and evenings

✅ Music & Entertainment categories dominate in average views

🛠 Future Enhancements
🧠 NLP-based title sentiment analysis

📈 Trend forecasting (time series analysis)

